AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002218> "OBSOLETE x has participant y if and only if x realizes some active role that inheres in y")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000117> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002218> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-6601-2165>)
