# Object Property: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002222> (temporally related to)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000114> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002222> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000125>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000117> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002222> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-6601-2165>)
