ObjectPropertyRange(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002414> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000015>)

# Object Property: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002418> (causally upstream of or within)

