# Object Property: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002431> (involved in or involved in regulation of)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002431> "c involved in or regulates p if and only if either (i) c is involved in p or (ii) c is involved in regulation of p")
