AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0003000> "Note that this definition doesn't quite distinguish the output of a transformation process from a production process, which is related to the identity/granularity issue.")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0003000> "produces"@en)
InverseObjectProperties(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0003000> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0003001>)
