# Object Property: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0010002> (is carrier of)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000112> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0010002> "Molecules of DNA are carriers of genetic information.")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000112> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0010002> "This copy of *War and Peace* is carrier of the novel written by Tolstoy.")
