AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000228> "The term has been replaced by a term imported from another ontology."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000228> "This is to be used when the original term has been replaced by a term imported from an other ontology. The deprecated term should reference the imported term with obo:IAO_0100001."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/contributor> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000228> <https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6875-5360>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/contributor> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000228> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-7356-1779>)
